t%20took%20about%20a%20month%20of%20being%20in%20Guangzhou%20to%20realize%20I%20was%20never%20moving%20back%20to%20England%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aidan%20Fairhall%20in%20Guangzhou%20in%202019%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579670f7a3c8094d5dc62c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAidan%20Fairhall%20in%20Guangzhou%20in%202019%3Cp%3EAidan%20Fairhall%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20England%2C%20I%20was%20teaching%20in%20schools%20in%20pretty%20deprived%20areas%20%E2%80%94%20where%20around%2070%25%20of%20students%20were%20on%20free%20meals%20as%20they%20were%20under%20the%20poverty%20line.%20The%20workload%20was%20intense%2C%20preparing%20eight%20curricula%20weekly%20for%20students%20with%20lots%20of%20behavioral%20needs.%20It%20felt%20like%20crowd%20control%20and%20constantly%20redirecting%20this%20torrent%20of%20energy%20that's%20always%20blasting%20at%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Guangzhou%2C%20the%20job%20was%20so%20wildly%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20taught%20at%20an%20international%20school%2C%20where%20the%20kids%20were%20well-behaved.%20I%20had%20only%20three%20different%20types%20of%20classes%20to%20prepare%20for.%20And%20class%20sizes%20were%2010%20to%2020%20students%2C%20much%20less%20than%20the%20over%2030%20you'd%20typically%20have%20in%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20meant%20rediscovering%20what%20work-life%20balance%20was.%20When%20I%20was%20in%20England%2C%20I'd%20mostly%20just%20travel%20back%20to%20my%20hometown%20for%20the%20holidays.%20In%20Guangzhou%2C%20I%20was%20spending%20weekends%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20renting%20out%20junk%20boats%20for%2040-person%20parties%20%E2%80%94%20and%20flying%20out%20to%20Taiwan%2C%20India%2C%20and%20Southeast%20Asia%20for%20vacations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22812%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aidan%20Fairhall%20c