0imagined%20Guangzhou%20was%20going%20be%20like%20the%20claustrophobic%20grandeur%20of%20Hong%20Kong%20where%20you%20could%20look%20up%20and%20see%20only%20a%20square%20of%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Guangzhou%20was%20made%20on%20a%20different%20scale%2C%20like%20a%20city%20made%20for%20giants.%20You%20could%20have%2015%20people%20walking%20abreast.%20I%20didn't%20expect%20how%20lush%20it%20was%2C%20like%20a%20city%20growing%20out%20of%20a%20jungle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20that%20first%20day%20in%20Guangzhou%2C%20another%20foreign%20teacher%20and%20I%20ventured%20out%20to%20a%20Chinese%20hotpot%20restaurant%20despite%20knowing%20zero%20Chinese.%20We%20didn't%20have%20a%20VPN%2C%20so%20we%20couldn't%20connect%20to%20anything.%20And%20there%20weren't%20image%20translators%20like%20Google%20Translate%20at%20the%20time%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20gesture%20and%20point%20for%20the%20waiters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20around%20us%20was%20giggling%20as%20things%20were%20being%20brought%20out%2C%20and%20we%20went%20back%20to%20that%20same%20restaurant%20every%20week%20after%20that.%20It%20was%20fantastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aidan%20Fairhall%20visiting%20a%20colleague's%20hometown%20near%20Changsha%20in%202018.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65796b8750edbc52a863a130%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAidan%20Fairhall%20visiting%20a%20colleague's%20hometown%20near%20Changsha%20in%202018.%3Cp%3EAidan%20Fairhall%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20struck%20me%20about%20expats%20who%20don't%20like%20living%20in%20China%20is%20that%20many%20have%20this%20idea%20that%20they%20can%20impose%20their%20pre-existing%20norms%20on%20life%20here.%20And%20they%20couldn't%20get%20past%20how%20people%20didn't%20do%20things%20the%20same%20way%20as%20in%20their%20home%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20food%2C%20for%20example.%20I've%20fallen%20in%20love%20with%20chicken%20feet%2C%20and%20I've%20traded%20in%20my%20typical%20Sunday%20roast%20for%20dim%20sum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20there%20were%20stumbling%20blocks.%20There's%20the%20uncertain%20quality%20of%20food%20in%20some%20places.%20It%20took%20some%20time%20to%20get%20used%20to%20doing%20so%20much%20digitally%2C%20and%20to%20the%20prevalence%20of%20online%20scams.%20I%20didn't%20use%20Taobao%2C%20an%20eCommerce%20site%2C%20for%20years%20because%20I%20just%20didn't%20understand%20which%20buttons%20to%20press.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENow%2C%20I%20feel%20reverse%20culture%20shock%20when%20I'm%20back%20home%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aidan%20Fairhall%20exploring%20the%20villages%20of%20Kaiping%2C%20Guangdong%20in%202016.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65796b0c0ec98e92f74edb83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAidan%20Fairhall%20exploring%20the%20villages%20of%20Kaiping%2C%20Guangdong%20in%202016.%3Cp%3EAidan%20Fairhall%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20schools%20I've%20worked%20for%20pay%20for%20return%20flights%20back%20to%20teachers'%20home%20countries%2C%20which%20means%20I%20get%20to%20go%20back%20to%20England%20every%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20time%20I%20go%20back%2C%20so%20much%20of%20England%20feels%20archaic%20to%20me.%20From%20how%20unclean%20and%20inefficient%20London's%20tube%20is%20compared%20to%20the%20metro%20systems%20in%20China%3B%C2%A0to%20how%20ridiculous%20it%20is%20to%20have%20your%20trousers%20weighed%20down%20by%20pockets%20full%20of%20change%20when%20we%20mostly%20go%20cashless%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20decade%20in%20China%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20part%20of%20the%20furniture%20here%20%E2%80%94%20whereas%20back%20home%2C%20I%20now%20feel%20out%20of%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20moved%20away%2C%20I%20had%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20friends.%20And%20despite%20promising%20them%20that%20I%20would%20definitely%20be%20back%20before%20I%20turned%2030%2C%20so%20I%20could%20be%20there%20for%20their%20kids%20and%20weddings%2C%20I%20can't%20quite%20see%20myself%20giving%20up%20my%20life%20here%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-england-to-china-teacher-9-years-relocation-comparison-essay-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703939821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579705a0ec98e92f74edbd8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-england-to-china-teacher-9-years-relocation-comparison-essay-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20employer%20pays%20for%20me%20to%20fly%20home%20every%20summer%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20reverse%20culture%20shock%20every%20time%20I'm%20back%20in%20England.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22teokaixiang%40protonmail.com%20(Kai%20Xiang%20Teo)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-england-to-china-teacher-9-years-relocation-comparison-essay-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Take%20a%20tour%20of%20Georgia's%20%2480%20million%20football%20center%2C%20which%20was%20built%20to%20be%20a%20'one-stop%20shop'%20for%20college%20football's%20top%20stars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20the%20multi-level%20weight%20room%20at%20Georgia's%20Butts-Mehre%20Heritage%20Hall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f631bab6f2ebb11f7ee03%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20multi-level%20weight%20room%20at%20Georgia's%20Butts-Mehre%20Heritage%20Hall.%3Cp%3EHOK%2FChristy%20Radecic%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C