26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f2fc2ab6f2ebb11f7e3c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20dining%20area%20is%20designed%20to%20look%20like%20a%20sports%20bar%20dubbed%20%26quot%3BBones%20Cafe.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EHOK%2FChristy%20Radecic%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20other%20comparable%20programs%20offer%20massive%20cafeteria-style%20dining%20halls%20for%20players%2C%20coaches%2C%20and%20staff.%20But%20with%20limited%20space%20to%20build%20at%20Georgia%2C%20HOK%20and%20the%20university%20were%20forced%20to%20get%20creative%20with%20the%20dining%20options%20for%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20was%20%26quot%3BBones%20Cafe%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20space%20designed%20to%20resemble%20a%20sports%20bar%20or%20casual%20restaurant%20with%20food%20available%20all%20day%20long.%20Bechtold%20says%20the%20move%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bhugely%20successful%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20Bulldogs%2C%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bcasual%20setting%20draws%20everybody%20in%20from%20players%20to%20coaches%20to%20support%20staff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20other%20thing%20with%20the%20relaxed%20opportunity%20for%20them%20to%20come%20and%20use%20the%20space%20is%20that%20they%20enjoy%20it%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Bechtold%20added.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20relief%20to%20where%20they%20may%20have%20more%20open%20conversations%20with%20their%20trainer%20or%20with%20their%20coach%20or%20with%20the%20staff%20psychologist%2C%20whomever%20may%20be%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere's%20also%20a%20demonstration%20kitchen%20for%20teaching%20players%20how%20to%20prepare%20meals%20for%20themselves.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20demonstration%20kitchen%20at%20Bones%20Cafe.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f3300ab6f2ebb11f7e52f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20demonstration%20kitchen%20at%20Bones%20Cafe.%3Cp%3EHOK%2FChristy%20Radecic%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20players%20have%20access%20to%20pre-prepared%20meals%20and%20snacks%20throughout%20the%20day%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0both%20at%20Bones%20Cafe%20and%20at%20a%20nearby%20grab-and-go%20nutrition%20bar.%20But%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20make%20meals%20of%20their%20own%2C%20the%20program%20asked%20HOK%20to%20integrate%20a%20demonstration%20kitchen%20into%20Bones%20Cafe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBechtold%20said%20the%20dietician%20on%20staff%20%26quot%3Breally%20pushed%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20teaching%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20one%20thing%20that%20they%20talked%20about%20from%20day%20one%20is%20they%20don't%20want%20the%20players%20leaving%20college%20and%20having%20a%20lesser%20experience%20after%20they've%20left%2C%26quot%3B%20Bechtold%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20they're%20teaching%20them%20how%20to%20create%20all%20these%20meals%20that%20they're%20having%20on%20their%20own.%20So%20once%20they%20move%20on%2C%20they've%20got%20the%20opportunity%20and%20have%20that%20skillset.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAn%20expansive%20sports%20medicine%20wing%20offers%20in-house%20treatment%20options%20for%20injured%20athletes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222589%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20several%20imaging%20options%20on-site%20at%20Georgia's%20Butts-Mehre%20Heritage%20Hall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f4d4f1c5c7b8c9a0d0c25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221453%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20several%20imaging%20options%20on-site%20at%20Georgia's%20Butts-Mehre%20Heritage%20Hall.%3Cp%3EHOK%2FRoyal%20Key%20and%20Sports%20Dissected%20by%20Coiski%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20large%20portion%20of%20the%20new-look%20Butts-Mehre%20Heritage%20Hall%20is%20devoted%20to%20injury%20treatment%20and%20recovery.%20Thanks%20to%20a%20partnership%20with%20Piedmont%20Hospital%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0one%20of%20the%20largest%20healthcare%20groups%20in%20Georgia%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20football%20program%20is%20able%20to%20offer%20medical%20care%20for%20its%20players%20in-house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sports%20medicine%20area%20boasts%20hydrotherapy%20pools%2C%20X-ray%20and%20MRI%20machines%2C%20sensory%20deprivation%20and%20cryotherapy%20chambers%2C%20and%20long-term%20concussion%20recovery%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20those%20things%20that%20are%20becoming%20more%20and%20more%20important%20to%20the%20student%20athletes%2C%20the%20parents%2C%20all%20of%20that%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20health%20and%20safety%20of%20these%20athletes%2C%26quot%3B%20Bechtold%20said.%20%26quot%3BKnowing%20they've%20got%20something%20like%20a%20local%20hospital%20embedded%20in%20their%20building%20just%20gives%20people%20that%20peace%20of%20mind%20that%20it's%20that%20much%20better%20care%20than%20maybe%20they%20would've%20had%20otherwise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20spaces%20devoted%20to%20self-care%20for%20the%20team.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20barbershop%20inside%20Georgia's%20Butts-Mehre%20Heritage%20Hall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f5dffab6f2ebb11f7edf5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20barbershop%20inside%20Georgia's%20Butts-Mehre%20Heritage%20Hall.%3Cp%3EHOK%2FChristy%20Radecic%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Butts-Mehre%20Heritage%20Hall%20renovation%20was%20designed%20to%20be%20more%20than%20a%20football%20facility.%20As%20Bechtold%20told%20BI%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20one-stop%20shop%26quot%3B%20for%20athletes%20on%20the%20team%20and%20offer%20%26quot%3Ba%20place%20where%20they%20can%20get%20everything%20through%20the%20course%20of%20their%20day%20and%20not%20have%20to%20bounce%20around%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20places%20and%20take%20that%20extra%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20the%20football%20headquarters%20offers%20some%20unique%20amenities%20for%20players.%20There's%20even%20a%20barbershop%20adjacent%20to%20the%20locker%20room%20for%20a%20quick%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20auditorium%20fits%20the%20entire%20team%20for%20film%20sessions%20and%20group%20meetings.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20auditorium%20at%20Georgia's%20Butts-Mehre%20Heritage%20Hall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f48c51c5c7b8c9a0d0bac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20auditorium%20at%20Georgia's%20Butts-Mehre%20Heritage%20Hall.%3Cp%3EHOK%2FChristy%20Radecic%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20all-team%20auditorium%20at%20Butts-Mehre%20Heritage%20Hall%20is%20nearly%20twice%20the%20size%20of%20the%20Bulldogs'%20old%20room.%20Now%2C%20the%20whole%20team%20can%20fit%20in%20one%20space%20for%20meetings%2C%20film%20sessions%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeon%20numbers%20on%20each%20side%20wall%20indicate%20the%20years%20of%20Georgia's%20division%20and%20conference%20championships%2C%20while%20the%20back%20wall%20features%20the%20years%20the%20Bulldogs%20secured%20the%20national%20title.%20The%20design%20heavily%20features%20black%20and%20gray%20and%2C%20notably%2C%20does%20not%20feature%20very%20much%20red.%20That%20was%20intentional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20space%20is%20unique%3B%20every%20design%20is%20really%20catered%20to%20that%20culture%20and%20that%20environment%20and%20that%20local%20group%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Bechtold%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20probably%20notice%20in%20Georgia%20there's%20some%20red%20and%20there's%20some%20black%2C%20but%20their%20team%20room%20or%20some%20of%20their%20spaces%20are%20more%20the%20grays%20and%20the%20blacks.%20And%20the%20team%2C%20as%20you%20can%20imagine%2C%20is%20always%20wearing%20their%20gear%20and%20color%20red%20and%20whatever%20else%2C%20so%20they%20bring%20the%20red%20into%20the%20picture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20weight%20room%2C%20which%20spans%202.5%20floors%2C%20is%20a%20sight%20to%20behold.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20weight%20room%20at%20Georgia's%20Butts-Mehre%20Heritage%20Hall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f3437ab6f2ebb11f7e5e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20weight%20room%20at%20Georgia's%20Butts-Mehre%20Heritage%20Hall.%3Cp%3EHOK%2FChristy%20Radecic%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20challenging%20aspect%20of%20the%20facility's%20vertical%20design%20was%20fitting%20a%20sufficiently%20sized%20weight%20room%20that%20didn't%20interfere%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20headquarters.%20Weight%20rooms%20tend%20to%20be%20pretty%20loud%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Byou%20don't%20want%20that%20sound%20and%20vibration%20transferring%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20building%20and%20causing%20headaches%20for%20everybody%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Bechtold%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20fit%20Georgia's%20weight%20room%20into%20the%20upper%20floors%20of%20the%20center%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20is%20something%20we%20oftentimes%20will%20try%20and%20avoid.%26quot%3B%20But%20HOK%20placed%20an%20equipment%20room%20directly%20underneath%20the%20weight%20room%20so%20that%20it%20could%20serve%20as%20something%20of%20%26quot%3Ba%20bunker.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20able%20to%20isolate%20that%20component%20and%20the%20structure%20of%20that%20weight%20room%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20building%2C%26quot%3B%20Bechtold%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20in%20doing%20that%2C%20we%20were%20sti