%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22There%20Was%20Time%20Lord%20Ram%20Was%20%26quot%3BLiving%20Under%20Tent%26quot%3B%2C%20But%20Now...%3A%20PM%20In%20Ayodhya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20arrived%20in%20a%20festooned%2C%20festive%20Ayodhya%20on%20Saturday%20to%20unveil%20a%20'new%20look%20old'%20city%20with%20an%20airport%2C%20a%20revamped%20train%20station%20and%20projects%20worth%20Rs%2015%2C700%20crore%20ahead%20of%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flower-bedecked%20temple%20town%2C%20associated%20with%20the%20Ramayana%20for%20centuries%20and%20at%20the%20centrestage%20of%20modern%20day%20politics%20since%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%2C%20was%20the%20cynosure%20of%20attention%20as%20PM%20Modi%20said%20the%20strength%20of%20'vikas'%20(development)%20and%20'virasat'%20(heritage)%20would%20take%20India%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20world%20is%20waiting%20for%20the%20historic%20moment%20of%20the%20'pran%20pratishtha'%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20here%20while%20appealing%20to%20people%20to%20not%20come%20on%20the%20day%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20the%20business%20of%20people%20from%20across%20the%20country%20and%20the%20world%20coming%20to%20Ayodhya%20had%20started%20and%20would%20go%20on%20till%20eternity%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20also%20appealed%20for%20a%20resolve%20to%20make%20town%20the%20cleanest%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20meeting%20after%20inaugurating%20the%20Maharshi%20Valmiki%20airport%20and%20the%20redeveloped%20station%20named%20Ayodhya%20Dham%20from%20where%20he%20flagged%20off%20two%20Amrit%20Bharat%20and%20six%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%2C%20some%20virtually%2C%20he%20appealed%20to%20all%20citizens%20to%20light%20diyas%20in%20their%20houses%20on%20January%2022%20so%20the%20whole%20country%20basks%20in%20the%20glory%20of%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarking%20January%2022%20as%20a%20special%20day%2C%20he%20also%20asked%20people%20to%20launch%20cleanliness%20drives%20at%20pilgrimage%20sites%20and%20temples%20across%20the%20country%20from%20Makar%20Sankranti%20on%20January%2014%20till%20the%20temple%20consecration%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20time%20Lord%20Ram%20was%20%26quot%3Bliving%20under%20a%20tent%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20now%20he%20will%20get%20a%20concrete%20house%20like%20the%20four%20crore%20poor%20who%20got%20pucca%20houses%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ujjwala%20scheme%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20transformed%20the%20lives%20of%20crores%20of%20mothers%20and%20sisters.%20Only%2014%20crore%20gas%20connections%20were%20given%20in%20five%20decades%2C%20but%20his%20government%20in%20a%20decade%20gave%2018%20crore%2C%20including%2010%20crore%20free%20of%20cost%20under%20the%20scheme%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20he%20stopped%20by%20at%20the%20home%20of%20an%20Ujjwala%20beneficiary%20Meera%20Majhi.%20He%20met%20the%20family%20in%20her%20humble%20home%20and%20was%20also%20seen%20drinking%20a%20cup%20of%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20inaugurated%2C%20dedicated%20to%20the%20nation%20and%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20of%20multiple%20development%20projects%20worth%20more%20than%20Rs%2015%2C700%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20comprise%20projects%20worth%20about%20Rs%2011%2C100%20crore%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20city%20and%20its%20surrounding%20areas%2C%20and%20those%20worth%20about%20Rs%204%2C600%20crore%20related%20to%20other%20works%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20which%20in%201992%20catapulted%20to%20global%20headlines%20with%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Mughal-era%20Babri%20Masjid%20by%20a%20group%20of%20kar%20sevaks%20who%20believed%20it%20was%20built%20on%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20was%20one%20of%20dances%2C%20music%20and%20the%20many%20folk%20colours%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20other%20states.%20After%20he%20arrived%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20PM%20Modi%20held%20a%20roadshow%20from%20the%20airport%20to%20the%20railway%20station%20and%20was%20greeted%20by%20hundreds%20of%20people%20lining%20alongside%20the%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20greeted%20people%20from%20his%20car%20and%20at%20one%20point%20opened%20the%20door%20of%20his%20vehicle%20to%20wave%20back%20at%20them.%20People%20showered%20flower%20petals%2C%20waved%20BJP%20flags%20and%20raised%20slogans%20in%20his%20praise.%20The%20prime%20minister%20also%20witnessed%20performances%20by%20cultural%20troupes%20along%20the%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath's%20office%20on%20Friday%20said%20that%20more%20than%201%2C400%20performers%20would%20present%20folk%20art%20and%20cultural%20programmes%20on%2040%20stages%20along%20the%20route%20from%20the%20airport%20to%20the%20railway%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20one%20group%20of%20women%20from%20Rajasthan%20danced%20the%20'Chakri'%20to%20lilting%20tunes%2C%20another%20from%20Prayagraj%20performed%20the%20ancient%20folk%20dance%20'Dedhiya'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20believed%20that%20women%20of%20Prayagraj%20danced%20the%20'Dedhiya'%20when%20Ramji%20and%20others%20had%20returned%20from%20Lanka%20after%20Lanka%20Dahan.%20Now%2C%20Ram%20Lalla%20is%20also%20getting%20a%20new%20temple%2C%20so%20the%20divine%20feeling%20have%20come%20back%2C%20so%20this%20performance.%20As%20also%20to%20welcome%20the%20PM%2C%26quot%3B%20lead%20dancer%20Preeti%20Singh%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inauguration%20of%20the%20airport%20and%20railway%20station%20took%20place%20after%20the%20roadshow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20inaugurating%20the%20station%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20took%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20facility.%20He%20was%20accompanied%20by%20Adityanath%2C%20Railway%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20and%20others.%20PM%20Modi%20was%20briefed%20by%20Vaishnaw%20about%20the%20station%2C%20the%20facade%20of%20which%20is%20inspired%20by%20traditional%20temple%20architecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Phase-I%20of%20the%20redeveloped%20station%20--%20Ayodhya%20Dham%20Junction%20Railway%20Station%20--%20has%20been%20completed%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%20240%20crore%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-storey%20railway%20station%20building%20is%20equipped%20with%20features%20such%20as%20lifts%2C%20escalators%2C%20food%20plazas%2C%20shops%20for%20puja%20needs%2C%20cloak%20rooms%2C%20child%20care%20rooms%20and%20waiting%20halls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20station%20building%20is%20%26quot%3Baccessible%20for%20all%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20%26quot%3BIGBC%20certified%20green%20station%20building%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20officials%20The%20prime%20minister%20visited%20the%20Lata%20Mangeshkar%20Chowk%2C%20where%20a%20giant-size%20veena%20has%20been%20installed.%20In%20keeping%20with%20the%20place%20and%20the%20mood%2C%20a%20bhajan%20by%20the%20late%20music%20queen%20played%20in%20the%20backdrop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20airport%2C%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Civil%20Aviation%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Civil%20Aviation%20Gen%20(Retired)%20VK%20Singh%20and%20Adityanath%20were%20among%20those%20who%20accompanied%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20facade%20of%20the%20terminal%20building%20depicts%20the%20architecture%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Ram%20temple%20here%2C%20while%20its%20interiors%20are%20decorated%20with%20paintings%20and%20murals%20depicting%20the%20life%20of%20Lord%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhase-1%20of%20the%20airport%20has%20been%20developed%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%201%2C450%20crore%2C%20according%20to%20officials.%20The%20airport's%20terminal%20building%20will%20have%20an%20area%20of%206%2C50