nancial%20distress%20in%20credit%20cards%20and%20auto%20loans%20reaches%20levels%20we%20last%20saw%20in%20the%202008%20Global%20Financial%20Crisis.%20The%20delinquent%20payments%20on%20these%20loans%20are%20expected%20to%20rise%20even%20further%20as%20layoffs%20increase%20and%20banks%20tighten%20their%20lending%20conditions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E5.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20in%20a%20'soft%20landing'%20all%20year%20long%2C%20as%20was%20the%20case%20in%201979%2C%201989%2C%202000%20and%202007.%20The%20'soft%20landing'%20is%20the%20transition%20phase%20%E2%80%94%20the%20bridge%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20expansion%20phase%20of%20the%20business%20cycle%20to%20the%20contraction%20phase%2C%20which%20I%20believe%20will%20be%20next%20year's%20story.%20The%20Fed%20has%20locked%20itself%20into%20a%20downturn.%26quot%3B%20(Rosenberg%20predicted%20the%20aggressive%20fiscal%20stimulus%20in%202023%20would%20depress%20year-on-year%20growth%2C%20and%20underlined%20the%20delayed%20impacts%20of%20the%20most%20extreme%20rate-hiking%20cycle%20in%20four%20decades.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-david-rosenberg-santa-hangover-economy-recession-2024-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703939101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658eb75cab6f2ebb11f7a442%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-david-rosenberg-santa-hangover-economy-recession-2024-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stock%20investors%20face%20a%20%26quot%3Bnasty%20January%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20US%20economy%20is%20showing%20cracks%20based%20on%20recent%20data%2C%20David%20Rosenberg%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40insider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fst