ew.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESuccessful%20people%20like%20Oprah%2C%20Bill%20Gates%2C%20Warren%20Buffett%2C%20and%20Elon%20Musk%20all%20allegedly%20follow%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20tried%20it%20for%20a%20month%20and%20started%20an%20online%20course.%20Still%2C%20I%20found%20the%20hard%20rule%20stressful.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20a%20huge%20shocker%20that%20successful%20people%20like%20Oprah%20Winfrey%2C%20Bill%20Gates%2C%20and%20Warren%20Buffett%20all%20spend%20their%20free%20time%20reading%20and%20learning%20new%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bigger%20mystery%20is%20how%20they%20have%20the%20self-discipline%20to%20soak%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBusinessInsider%2Fstatus%2F1121033548314611712%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E600-1%2C000%20pages%20a%20day%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20Buffett%20says%20he%20did%20early%20in%20his%20career.%20As%20much%20as%20I%20value%20an%20educational%20non-fiction%20read%2C%20I%20usually%20would%20rather%20see%20a%20friend%2C%20cuddle%20my%20cat%2C%20or%20scroll%20through%20Instagram%20videos%20of%20other%20people's%20cats%20after%20a%20demanding%20work%20day.%20And%20if%20my%20net%20worth%20was%20in%20the%20billions%E2%80%A6%20I'm%20sorry%2C%20but%20what%20are%20books%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-gifts-billionaires-worlds-richest-hermes-bags-travel-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMy%20Birkin%20and%20I%20are%20in%20space%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurns%20out%2C%20both%20today's%20wealthiest%20people%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-net-worth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20O.G.%20thought%20leaders%20like%20Benjamin%20Frankin%20owe%20part%20of%20their%20success%20to%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbill-gates-warren-buffet-and-oprah-all-use-the-5-hour-rule-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E5-hour%20rule%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20they%20spend%20at%20least%20one%20hour%20a%20day%2C%20five%20days%20a%20week%20reading%2C%20reflecting%2C%20and%20experimenting%20with%20new%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20spirit%20of%20starting%20a%20new%20year%20strong%2C%20I%20tried%20following%20the%20rule%20for%20a%20month.%20While%20it%20was%20harder%20than%20I%20expected%20(an%20hour%20is%20a%20long%20time%20when%20you're%20already%20supposed%20to%20work%20eight%20of%20them)%2C%20it%20also%20got%20me%20to%20start%20a%20few%20things%20I%20had%20put%20off%20for%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20finally%20started%20an%20online%20course%20I%20eyed%20for%20years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taking%20an%20online%20course%20in%20digital%20marketing%20led%20by%20Google.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f1c651c5c7b8c9a0cf812%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaking%20an%20online%20course%20in%20digital%20marketing%20led%20by%20Google.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%205-hour%20rule%20is%20a%20fairly%20loose%20one%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20myself%20a%20few%20concrete%20options%20for%20things%20I%20could%20spend%20my%20hour%20on.%20The%20goal%20was%20to%20have%20some%20structure%2C%20while%20not%20locking%20myself%20into%20something%20that%20might%20get%20too%20tedious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20told%20myself%20I%20could%20spend%20my%20daily%20hour%20on%20reading%2C%20weightlifting%2C%20writing%2C%20and%20career-planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20an%20online%20course%20in%20digital%20marketing%20%E2%80%94%20a%20subject%20I've%20been%20interested%20in%20and%20thought%20could%20apply%20to%20my%20job%20in%20some%20way.%20Because%20digital%20marketing%20is%20very%20new%20to%20me%2C%20I%20found%20it%20the%20most%20engaging%20to%20pick%20up%20on%20lunch%20breaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20drive%20myself%20to%20go%20to%20the%20gym%2C%20I%20combined%20two%20options%20and%20put%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Subtle%20Art%20of%20Not%20Giving%20a%20F*ck%26quot%3B%20audiobook%20while%20I%20worked%20out.%20It%20proved%20to%20be%20exactly%20the%20kind%20of%20messaging%20I%20needed%20when%20I%20felt%20self-conscious%20about%20using%20the%20lat%20pulldown%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20do%20anything%20else%2C%20I%20just%20made%20my%20way%20through%20a%20464-page%20advanced%20copy%20of%20%26quot%3BHow%20to%20ADHD%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20book%20I%20was%20reading%20for%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20break%20up%20the%20hour%20to%20make%20it%20more%20manageable%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20challenge%20of%20sticking%20to%20the%20rule%20was%20devoting%20a%20solid%20hour%20of%20time%20every%20day.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20would%20stick%20to%20the%20full%20hour%2C%20but%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20I%20divided%20it%20into%2020-minute%20chunks%2C%20reading%20pages%20of%20my%20book%20or%20squeezing%20in%20course%20videos%20when%20I%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20following%20more%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fpomodoro-technique%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epomodoro%20technique%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20is%20based%20on%20the%20idea%20that%20most%20people%20can%20stay%20focused%20for%20up%20to%2025%20minutes%20at%20a%20time.%20The%20online%20course%20especially%20worked%20well%20for%20this%2C%20since%20it's%20self-paced%20and%20broken%20down%20into%20lots%20of%20smaller%20videos%20and%20quizzes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDid%20I%20always%20spend%20exactly%20an%20hour%20each%20day%3F%20Look%2C%20I%20draw%20the%20line%20at%20anxiously%20timing%20myself%20with%20a%20stopwatch.%20The%20important%20thing%20is%20I%20read%20more%20actually%20useful%20content%20than%20petty%20social%20media%20takes%2C%20which%20is%20a%20miracle%20in%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20treat%20the%20rule%20as%20more%20of%20a%20goal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20life%20got%20in%20the%20way%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20that%20was%20a%20bad%20thing.%20My%20experiment%20coincided%20with%20the%20holidays%2C%20which%20meant%20I%20wanted%20to%20figure%20out%20gifts%2C%20host%20dinner%20parties%20with%20friends%2C%20or%20just%20spend%20my%20nights%20with%20my%20and%20my%20fianc%C3%A9's%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20failure%2C%20but%20truthfully%2C%20I%20don't%20get%20the%20point%20of%20optimizing%20myself%20so%20much%20that%20I%20miss%20out%20on%20the%20whole%20point%20of%20being%20successful%20in%20the%20first%20place%3A%20Being%20able%20to%20relax%20and%20enjoy%20people's%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20the%20idea%20of%20the%205-hour%20rule%20as%20more%20of%20a%20guideline%20to%20strive%20for%2C%20but%20not%20beat%20myself%20up%20over%20when%20I%20don't%20hit%20it.%20Maybe%20that%20means%20I%20won't%20ever%20be%20rich%20enough%20to%20fly%20to%20Mars%2C%20but%20I%20think%20I'm%20on%20to%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-5-hour-rule-bill-gates-oprah-improvement-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703938801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f16e5ab6f2ebb11f7d5ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-5-hour-rule-bill-gates-oprah-improvement-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%205-hour%20rule%2C%20followed%20by%20Oprah%2C%20Warren%20Buffett%2C%20and%20Bill%20Gates%2C%20is%20about%20devoting%20one%20hour%20a%20day%2C%20five%20days%20a%20week%2C%20to%20learning%20something%20new.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpugachevsky%40insider.com%20(Julia%20Pugachevsky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busin