tion%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%20recalled%20that%20he%20had%20visited%20Ayodhya%20even%20when%20he%20was%20chief%20minister%20of%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20veiled%20swipe%20at%20BJP%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20only%20expect%20that%20political%20event%20shouldn't%20be%20made%20out%20of%20it%20(the%20consecration%20ceremony).%20Lord%20Ram%20is%20not%20the%20property%20of%20any%20single%20party.%20This%20is%20the%20matter%20of%20faith%20for%20crores%20of%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20it%20was%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%20that%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20Ram%20temple%20and%20the%20Centre%20had%20no%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20spokesperson%20Sanjay%20Raut%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Btop%20ten%26quot%3B%20among%20those%20accused%20of%20demolishing%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20in%201992%20are%20Shiv%20Sainiks%20including%20Bal%20Thackeray.%20%26quot%3BA%20total%20of%20109%20Shiv%20Sainikas%20from%20Maharashtra%20figure%20in%20the%20list%20of%20the%20accused%20persons%20in%20the%20demolition%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20and%20more%20than%206%2C000%20people%20are%20expected%20to%20attend%20the%20consecration%20ceremony.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703936940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2F40kimiec_uddhav-thackeray-650_625x300_06_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdont-need-invitation-to-visit-ayodhya-uddhav-thackeray-on-attending-ram-temple-event-4769953%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uddhav%20Thackeray%20stressed%20he%20doesn't%20need%20a%20formal%20invite%20as%20Ra