%2C%20%26quot%3BLooking%20Ahead%202024.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EParth%20Raval%20is%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20planning%2C%20especially%20at%20a%20company%20like%20PepsiCo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPepsi%20created%20the%20growth%20office%20about%20three%20years%20ago%20as%20the%20organization%20got%20bigger%20and%20more%20complex.%20As%20chief%20growth%20officer%20for%20PepsiCo%20Foods%20North%20America%2C%20Raval%20has%20to%20balance%20the%20short%20term%20with%20the%20long%20term.%20He's%20responsible%20for%20brands%20including%20Quaker%20and%20Frito-Lay%2C%20and%20he%20says%20his%20favorite%20Pepsi%20product%20is%20nacho-cheese%20Doritos%20(%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20classic%20item!%26quot%3B).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20factors%20like%20high%20interest%20rates%2C%20higher-than-normal%20inflation%2C%20and%20the%20resumption%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-payments-debt-service-cost-consumer-spending-economic-outlook-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudent-loan%20repayment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3Bhow%20we%20spend%20and%20use%20our%20money%20is%20changing%2C%26quot%3B%20Raval%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BEverything%20costs%20more%2C%20and%20all%20organizations%20have%20been%20struggling%20with%20trying%20to%20get%20it%20exactly%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20everyone%20wants%20lower%20prices%20and%20high-quality%20items%2C%20Raval%20said%20he'd%20noticed%20some%20differences%20across%20generations.%20Older%20generations%2C%20particularly%20boomers%2C%20want%20foods%20that%20are%20lower%20in%20sodium%20and%20healthier.%20Millennials%20and%20Gen%20Zers%20are%20looking%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffood-trends-spicy-food-pickles-cold-coffee-buffalo-wings-grubhub-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20lot%20more%20flavor%2C%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaval's%20insights%20are%20part%20of%20Business%20Insider's%20year-end%20leadership%20package%2C%20%26quot%3BLooking%20Ahead%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20digging%20into%20vision%2C%20strategy%2C%20and%20challenges%20across%20corporate%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20you%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20most%20for%202024%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContinuing%20to%20build%20out%20and%20accelerate%20agendas%20around%20longer-range%20planning%20across%20supply%20and%20demand%2C%20and%20using%20technology%20to%20help%20us%20be%20more%20granular.%20This%20is%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20looking%20to%20leverage%20some%20technology%20vendor%20partners%20to%20start%20to%20build%20a%20much%20more%20sophisticated%20medium-%20and%20long-term%20forecasting%20engine.%20The%20fluctuations%20between%20supply%20and%20demand%20are%20part%20of%20the%20new%20normal%2C%20and%20we%20have%20to%20get%20much%20more%20deliberate%20and%20more%20sophisticated%20with%20our%20medium-%20and%20long-term%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20area%20that%20I'm%20pretty%20excited%20about%20is%20thinking%20about%20our%20innovation%20and%20what%20matters%20most%20to%20our%20consumers.%20The%20key%20difference%20here%20is%20that%20we're%20not%20siloed.%20Even%20in%20the%20design%20of%20different%20products%2C%20we%20think%20about%20the%20implications%20across%20the%20chain%20in%20a%20much%20more%20deliberate%20way%2C%20but%20keep%20the%20consumer%20at%20the%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pandemic%20pulled%20the%20future%20forward%20by%20three%20to%20four%20years%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpost-coronavirus-more-americans-will-shop-online-for-groceries-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20respect%20to%20where%20shoppers%20purchase%20their%20products%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%20now%20we're%20focused%20on%20building%20what%20I%20call%20%26quot%3B