BJP%20is%20resorting%20to%20dubious%20tricks%20to%20damage%20Nitish%20%3Cem%3Eji%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3Es%20image.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERealistically%2C%20it%20is%20the%20BJP%20that%20is%20in%20troubled%20waters%20in%20Bihar%20after%20Nitish%20deserted%20it%20in%20August%202022%20and%20joined%20the%20Mahagathbandhan.%20It%20is%20an%20electorally%20proven%20reality%20that%20the%20RJD%20enjoys%20impregnable%20hold%20on%20the%20Yadavs%20and%20Muslims%20who%20together%20constitute%20over%2031%25%20of%20the%20voters%2C%20and%20Nitish%20enjoys%20the%20same%20over%20the%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%20(EBCs)%20who%20are%2036.01%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20report.%20Nitish%20has%20increased%20his%20hold%20over%20this%20population%20by%20raising%20their%20reservation%20in%20government%20jobs%20from%2018%25%20to%2025%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20hard%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20make%20inroads%20into%20the%20OBC%20and%20EBC%E2%80%99s%20social%20base%20empowered%20and%20nursed%20well%2C%20earlier%20by%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20now%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20The%20BJP%20is%2C%20apparently%20playing%20all%20the%20tricks%20to%20foment%20differences%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Mahagathbandhan%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20weaken%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703935863000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30165226%2FEffect-47.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnitish-returns-as-jdu-chief-move-to-strengthen-india-or-possible-re-entry-into-the-nda-fold%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20are%20multiple%20theories%20going%20around%20over%20the%20change%20of%20guard%20in%20Janata%20Dal%20(United).%20While%20some%20say%20the%20move%20is%20to%20bring%20coherence%20to%20the%20campaign%20of%20INDIA%2C%20others%20say%20the%20development%20should%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20light%20of%20Nitish%20being%20'peeved'%20at%20I