%2022%20people%20who%20want%20her%20to%20hand%20the%20billion%20to%20a%20group%20that%20donates%20money%20to%20Russians%20fighting%20in%20Ukraine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Balmost%20naked%26quot%3B%20party%20was%20held%20on%20December%2020.%20Footage%20from%20the%20event%20showed%20a%20number%20of%20well-known%20Russian%20personalities%2C%20including%20pop%20stars%20Filipp%20Kirkorov%2C%20Lolita%20and%20Dima%20Bilan%2C%20as%20well%20as%20TV%20host%20and%202018%20presidential%20candidate%20Ksenia%20Sobchak%2C%20dressed%20in%20underwear%20and%20lingerie.%20Rapper%20Vacio%2C%20real%20name%20Nikolai%20Vasilyev%2C%20was%20also%20seen%20with%20only%20a%20sock%20covering%20his%20modesty.%20He%20has%20since%20been%20jailed%20for%2015%20days%20and%20fined%20200%2C000%20roubles%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frussian-celebrities-fined-and-jailed-over-almost-naked-nightclub-party-13039282%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESky%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Foutrage-over-almost-naked-party-in-russia-attended-by-many-celebrities-4722949%5C%22%3Ecritics%20of%20the%20event%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20party%20was%20against%20the%20country's%20conservative%20values.%20Taking%20to%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20Russian%20politician%20Maria%20Butina%20said%20that%20she%20has%20asked%20Russia's%20Ministry%20of%20Internal%20Affairs%20if%20the%20party%20complied%20with%20Russia's%20prohibition%20of%20LGBTQ%2B%20%26quot%3Bpropaganda%26quot%3B%2C%20or%20violated%20the%20order%20outlining%20%26quot%3Btraditional%20Russian%20spiritual%20and%20moral%20values%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYekaterina%20Mizulina%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20pressure%20group%20Free%20Internet%20League%2C%20called%20for%20a%20boycott%20of%20the%20attendees.%20%26quot%3BSuch%20hangouts%20are%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20foot%20of%20the%20entire%20policy%20pursued%20by%20the%20state.%20The%20partygoers%20live%20in%20a%20different%20world%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20on%20Telegram%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthese%20people%20should%20be%20boycotted%20at%20the%20state%20level%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703934060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F2t1cb8c_russia-almost-naked-party_625x300_22_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussian-influencer-anastasia-ivleeva-fined-for-hosting-almost-naked-party-in-moscow-4769708%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Russian%20TV%20presenter%20and%20influencer%20who%20sparked%20outrage%20for%20hosting%20an%20%26quot%3Balmost%20naked%26quot%3B%20party%20in%20Moscow%20has%20been%20fined%2C%20the%20BBC%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussian-influencer-anastasia-ivleeva-fined-for-hosting-almost-naked-party-in-moscow-4769708%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussian-influencer-anastasia-ivleeva-fined-for-hosting-almost-naked-party-in-moscow-4769708%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussian-influencer-anastasia-ivleeva-fined-for-hosting-almost-naked-party-in-moscow-4769708%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20military%20says%2013%20Ukrainian%20rockets%20downed%20in%20southern%20Belgorod%20region%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703933964000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106403112%2Cimgsize-1571804.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussian-military-says-13-ukrainian-rockets-downed-in-southern-belgorod-region%2Farticleshow%2F106403029.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F