png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EFive%20cases%20registered%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Pathalgadi%20movement%20in%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Kunti%20district%20are%20still%20pending%20to%20be%20withdrawn.%20Four%20years%20ago%2C%20in%20December%202019%2C%20when%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20current%20chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20took%20over%2C%20he%20vowed%20to%20withdraw%20all%20cases%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20movement%2C%20filed%20under%20his%20predecessor%20Raghubar%20Das%E2%80%99s%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20total%2021%20cases%20registered%20by%20Das%E2%80%99s%20government%20in%20Khunti%2C%2016%20so%20far%20have%20been%20withdrawn%20under%20the%20Soren%20government.%20In%20March%202020%2C%20the%20Soren%20government%20going%20against%20its%20promise%20filed%20a%20new%20case%20against%20the%20movement.%20The%20pending%20cases%20name%20Stan%20Swamy%20along%20with%2020%20other%20activists%20and%20intellectuals%20associated%20with%20the%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20information%20regarding%20pending%20cases%20has%20been%20disclosed%20by%20replies%20received%20to%20appeals%20filed%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act%2C%20said%20Jharkhand%20Janadhikar%20Mahasabha%20in%20a%20press%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2029%20December%202019%2C%20when%20Soren%20right%20after%20taking%20the%20oath%20as%20chief%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fprdjharkhand%2Fstatus%2F1211287224005869574%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fprdjharkhand%2Fstatus%2F1211287224005869574%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1704003291869000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3j-rVqc82fALGEMexM9eft%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20all%20Pathalgadi%20cases%2C%20it%20was%20met%20with%20widespread%20appreciation%20and%20support.%20The%20earlier%20Jharkhand%20government%2C%20headed%20by%20Das%2C%20had%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Pathalgadi%C2%A0movement%20and%20responded%20with%20severe%20violence%20and%20repression.%20It%20had%20filed%20several%20cases%20against%20the%20people%20associated%20with%20the%20movement%20and%20also%20several%20Adivasi%20traditional%20heads%20of%20the%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20filed%20several%20cases%20against%20about%20200%20named%20accused%20and%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20unnamed%20people%20under%20charges%20that%20included%20abetment%2C%20obstruction%20to%20public%20servants%20discharging%20their%20duty%2C%20creation%20of%20public%20nuisance%2C%20criminal%20intimidation%2C%20and%20even%20sedition.%20As%20many%20as%2028%20first%20information%20reports%20(FIRs)%20related%20to%20the%20P%3Cspan%3Eathalgadi%3C%2Fspan%3E%20movement%20were%20spread%20across%20Khunti%20(21)%2C%20Saraikela-Kharsawan%20(5)%2C%20and%20West%20Singhbhum%20(2)%20districts%20were%20registered%20by%20the%20Raghubar%20Das%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20allegations%20that%20the%20Soren%20government%20is%20yet%20to%20address%20the%20issues%20raised%20during%20the%20%3Cspan%3EPathalgadi%3C%2Fspan%3E%20movement%2C%20such%20as%20widespread%20violation%20of%20special%20laws%20and%20provisions%20for%20Adivasis%20(PESA%2C%20Fifth%20Schedule%2C%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%2C%20CNT%20Act%2C%20etc.)%2C%20marginalisation%20of%20Adivasi%20worldview%2C%20exploitation%20of%20Adivasis%20by%20the%20police%2C%20administration%2C%20and%20non-Adivasis%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jharkhand%20Janadhikar%20Mahasabha%20has%20been%20demanding%20the%20Soren%20government%20to%20immediately%20withdraw%20all%20five%20pending%20%3Cspan%3EPathalgadi%3C%2Fspan%3E%20cases%2C%20initiate%20action%20against%20human%20rights%20violations%20in%20Khunti%2C%20and%20award%20compensation%20to%20victims.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20calling%20for%20the%20strict%20implementation%20of%20special%20laws%20and%20provisions%20for%20Adivasis%20such%20as%20PESA%2C%20Fifth%20Schedule%2C%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%2C%20CNT%20Act%2C%20and%20so%20on%20in%20letter%20and%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703930056000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F22171455%2FScreen-Shot-2019-07-22-at-3.48.58-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F4-years-after-announcement-soren-govt-yet-to-withdraw-cases-pending-against-pathalgadi-movement%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20pending%20cases%20name%20Stan%20Swamy%20along%20with%2020%20other%20activists%20and%20intellectuals%20associated%20with%20the%20movement.%C2%A0On%2029%20December%202019%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%20soon%20after%20taking%20the%20oath%20as%20chief%20minister%20had%20announced%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20all%20Pathalgadi%20cases.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F4-years-after-announcement-soren-govt-yet-to-withdraw-cases-pending-against-pathalgadi-movement%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shami%20%26quot%3BTook%20Injections%26quot%3B%20During%20WC%3A%20Report%20Reveals%20Pacer's%20'Chronic%20Issue'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammed%20Shami%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1580-shami-ahmed-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Shami%3C%2Fa%3E's%20absence%20was%20heavily%20felt%20during%20India%20vs%20South%20Africa%20first%20Test.%20The%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20pacers%20leaked%20runs%20as%20South%20Africa%20batter%20piled%20on%20runs.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20did%20not%20have%20proper%20support%20as%20the%20likes%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammed%20Siraj%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107503-mohammed-siraj-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Siraj%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Prasidh%20Krishna%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107509-prasidh-krishna-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPrasidh%20Krishna%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shardul%20Thakur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63779-shardul-narendra-thakur-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShardul%20Thakur%3C%2Fa%3E%20failed%20to%20live%20up%20to%20the%20expectations.%20Mohammed%20Shami%2C%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023's%20highest%20wicket-taker%2C%20could%20have%20been%20handy%20in%20such%20a%20situation.%20However%2C%20he%20is%20nursing%20an%20injury%20and%20missed%20the%20series.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20report%20titled%2C%20%26quot%3BPrasidh's%20performance%20hints%20at%20bare%20bench%20strength%26quot%3B%20news%20agency%20PTI%20revealed%20that%20Shami%20played%20the%20World%20Cup%20with%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShami%20has%20a%20chronic%20left%20heel%20issue.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20don't%20know%20that%20he%20took%20injections%20regularly%20during%20World%20Cup%20and%20played%20the%20entire%20tournament%20through%20pain.%20But%20you%20must%20understand%20that%20as%20you%20grow%20older%2C%20recovery%20from%20each%20niggle%20or%20big%20injury%20takes%20that%20more%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20former%20Bengal%20teammate%20of%20Shami%2C%20aware%20of%20his%20situation%20told%20PTI%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Shami%20opened%20up%20on%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue's%20six-wicket%20loss%20against%20Australia%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%20final%20match%20and%20said%20that%20the%20nation%20was%20disappointed%20after%20the%20defeat.%20While%20speaking%20to%20the%20press%2C%20Shami%20said%20that%20the%20hosts%20gave%20their%20best%20to%20continue%20the%20momentum%20throughout%20the%20tournament%20and%20win%20the%20final%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2033-year-old%20added%20that%20they%20cannot%20explain%20where%20they%20went%20wrong%20during%20the%20final%20match%20of%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%20against%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20nation%20was%20disappointed%20(when%20India%20lost%20the%20World%20Cup).%20We%20tried%20hundred%20per%20cent%20to%20continue%20the%20momentum%20till%20the%20end%20that%20we%20had%20created%20and%20win%20the%20final.%20But...it%20cannot%20be%20explained%2C%20where%20we%20went%20wrong%20at%20the%20end...%2C%26quot%3B%20Shami%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20India's%20loss%2C%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20met%20the%20players%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%20and%20comforted%20them.%20The%20video%20of%20that%20meeting%20was%20widely%20shared.%20In%20that%20meeting%2C%20PM%20Modi%20hugged%20Shami%20and%20congratulated%20him%20for%20his%20performance.%20That%20video%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20and%20grabbed%20mixed%20reactions%20from%20the%20viewers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Aaj%20Tak%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Shami%20revealed%20that%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20players%20were%20not%20ready%20for%20the%20PM's%20visit%20as%20it%20came%20as%20a%20surprise%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20heartbroken%20after%20the%20loss%20and%20were%20sitting%20dejectedly.%20It%20was%20like%20our%20hard%20work%20of%20two%20months%20got%20negated%20due%20to%20just%20one%20match.%20It%20was%20our%20bad%20day%20and%20we%20were%20dejected%20but%20when%20the%20PM%20enters%2C%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20your%20head%20high.%20We%20were%20not%20even%20told%20that%20Modiji%20was%20coming%20there%20and%20suddenly%20he%20entered.%20Earlier%2C%20we%20were%20not%20even%20in%20the%20mood%20to%20eat%20and%20talk%20to%20each%20other%20but%20when%20he%20came%2C%20it%20was%20such%20a%20big%20surprise%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shami.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703929980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fppphhd48_shami-_625x300_02_December_23