-million-mansion-in-massachusetts%2Farticleshow%2F106399718.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lord%20Ram%20Doesn't%20Belong%20Only%20To%20Hindus%2C%20But%20Entire%20World%3A%20Farooq%20Abdullah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENational%20Conference%20Chief%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20today%20congratulated%20the%20people%20who%20have%20put%20efforts%20into%20making%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20saying%20that%20brotherhood%20in%20India%20is%20diminishing%20and%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20revive%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20the%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20chief%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAyodhya%20Ram%20Temple%20is%20about%20to%20be%20inaugurated.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20congratulate%20everyone%20who%20made%20the%20effort%20for%20the%20temple.%20It's%20ready%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20emphasised%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20doesn't%20only%20belong%20to%20Hindus%3B%20he%20belongs%20to%20everyone%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20want%20to%20say%20to%20the%20whole%20nation%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20doesn't%20only%20belong%20to%20Hindus%3B%20he%20belongs%20to%20everyone%20in%20the%20world.%20He%20is%20the%20Lord%20for%20all%20the%20people%20across%20the%20world.%20It's%20written%20in%20the%20books%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%20further%20said%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20has%20given%20a%20message%20of%20brotherhood%2C%20love%2C%20unity%20and%20helping%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Lord%20Rama)%20has%20given%20a%20message%20of%20brotherhood%2C%20love%2C%20unity%20and%20helping%20each%20other.%20He%20has%20always%20said%20to%20uplift%20the%20fallen%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20religion%20or%20ethnicity.%20He%20has%20given%20a%20universal%20message.%20Today%2C%20as%20this%20temple%20is%20about%20to%20be%20inaugurated%2C%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%20to%2