0amended%20act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20CAG%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETow%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20last%20bastion%20of%20resistance%20fell.%20Comptroller%20of%20Audit%20and%20Accounts%20was%20totally%20silenced%20in%20October%2C%20when%20Girish%20Murmu%2C%20a%20Gujarat%20cadre%20officer%2C%20was%20appointed%20as%20CAG%20in%20August%202020%2C%20it%20was%20seen%20as%20virtual%20death%20for%20CAG.%20For%2C%20Murmu%20was%20considered%20as%20a%20trusted%20Modi%20aide%20and%20principal%20secretary%20to%20him%20when%20he%20was%20chief%20minister.%20He%20had%20also%20worked%20with%20Amit%20Shah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20deep%20state%20within%20CAG%2C%20an%20institution%20of%20high%20repute%2C%20showed%20signs%20of%20occasional%20resistance.%20Murmu%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20was%20to%20concentrate%20on%20cases%20in%20opposition-ruled%20states%20and%20avoid%20central%20accounts.%20This%20was%20greatly%20successful.%20Despite%20this%2C%20the%20government%20was%20infuriated%20when%20CAG%20came%20out%20with%20a%20number%20reports%20critical%20of%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Modi%20establishment%20retaliated%20by%20allegedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Findia%2Fcag-auditors-transfer-congress-bharatmala-ayushman-bharat-bjp-18021751.htm%5C%22%3Etransferring%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20officials%20who%20prepared%20the%20offending%20reports.%20Their%20reports%20had%20dented%20the%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20claim%20of%20being%20a%20corruption-free%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20offending%20reports%20had%20brought%20out%20several%20irregularities%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20and%20Dwarka%20Expressway.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decline%20of%20CAG%20under%20Modi%20has%20been%20really%20disheartening.%20An%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.c