eg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Even%20after%2025%20days%20of%20winning%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20is%20yet%20to%20form%20its%20ministry%20in%20Rajasthan.%20According%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fdec%2F29%2Fno-raj-cabinet-25-days-after-victory-2645888.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20disagreements%20%E2%80%93%20between%20the%20RSS%20and%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20factions%2C%20and%20within%20the%20BJP%20in%20representing%20several%20castes%20in%20the%20state%20ministry%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20delay.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20winning%20party%20has%20taken%20such%20a%20long%20time%20in%20forming%20the%20ministry%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERift%20between%20two%20BJP%20factions%20in%20state%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajasthan%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Frajasthan-assembly%2Frajasthan-election-results-december-3-2023-bjp-congress-live-updates%2Farticle67597833.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Evoted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20BJP%20into%20power%20on%20December%203%20by%20a%20clear%20majority%2C%20winning%20115%20of%20the%20199%20seats%20it%20contested.%20On%20December%2012%2C%20the%20BJP%20announced%20that%20first-time%20MLA%20Bhajanlal%20Sharma%20will%20be%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20new%20chief%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%2025%20days%20later%2C%20the%20state%20ministry%20has%20still%20not%20been%20formed.%20%3C%2F