ce%20and%20got%20paid%20for%20the%20very%20first%20time.%20This%20is%20how%20I%20realised%20that%20I%20can%20pursue%20music%20as%20a%20professional%20career%20instead%20of%20studying%2C%20giving%20exams%2C%20and%20pursuing%20government%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20any%20artist%20starting%20out%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20pay%20for%20studio%20sessions%20when%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20it.%20Early%20on%2C%20Moko%20would%20borrow%20money%20from%20his%20mother%20to%20pay%20for%20these%20sessions%20because%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20proper%20recording%20studio%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsg1wDKPawL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsg1wDKPawL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsg1wDKPawL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Mvuko%20Koza%20(%40mokokoza)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInfinity%20Inc.%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20after%20earning%20his%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20(Physical)%20Anthropology%20in%202018%2C%20however%2C%20he%20got%20a%20call%20from%20Asalie%20Peseyie%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Dimapur-based%20record%20label%2C%20Infinity%20Inc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20first%20heard%20of%20Moko%20Koza%20back%20in%20late%202017%20after%20listening%20to%20a%20Nagamese%20track%20he%20released%20called%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dd_fOyfLMNo8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPuisa%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%20When%20I%20met%20him%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202018%2C%20I%20found%20a%20fully%20dedicated%20and%20humble%20individual%20%E2%80%94%20two%20characteristics%20that%20have%20remained%20constant%20since%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Asalie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Asalie%20was%20a%20rapper%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20and%20a%20pioneer%20of%20Hip%20Hop%20in%20Nagaland.%20But%20frustrated%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20support%20system%2C%20he%20traded%20in%20his%20mic%20for%20other%20pursuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInfinity%20Inc.%20stemmed%20from%20my%20short%20stint%20as%20a%20rapper%20earlier%20in%20the%202000s.%20The%20lack%20of%20a%20support%20system%20made%20it%20almost%20impossible%20for%20local%20artists%20to%20break%20out.%20Of%20course%2C%20social%20media%20was%20not%20even%20around%20at%20the%20time.%20These%20experiences%20inspired%20me%20to%20create%20Infinity%20Inc.%20%E2%80%94%20a%20springboard%20for%20upcoming%20Naga%20artists%20to%20reach%20the%20levels%20that%20they%20are%20capable%20of%20doing.%20At%20present%2C%20we%20have%20four%20artists%2C%20three%20DJs%20and%20two%20producers%20who%20are%20signed%20to%20our%20label%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEver%20since%20I%20started%20Infinity%20Inc.%20in%20February%202018%2C%20our%20priority%20was%20to%20sign%20Moko%20as%20an%20artist.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20appreciated%20that%20his%20art%20stems%20from%20his%20love%20of%20his%20culture%20and%20people%20and%20is%20marked%20by%20originality%20%E2%80%94%20a%20rare%20commodity%20in%20artists%20these%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Asalie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Moko%20remembers%20the%20call%20he%20received%20from%20Asalie%20following%20his%20post-graduation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20call%2C%20Assalie%20told%20me%20how%20they%20wanted%20to%20sign%20me%20as%20an%20artist.%20Without%20any%20second%20thoughts%2C%20I%20signed%20with%20them%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20music.%20Joining%20Infinity%20Inc.%20gave%20me%20access%20to%20a%20professional%20studio%20with%20in-house%20producers%20and%20sound%20engineers%20who%20would%20help%20me%20make%20the%20music%20I%20wanted.%20From%20struggling%20early%20on%20to%20put%20out%20music%20and%20asking%20my%20mother%20for%20money%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20studio%20session%2C%20today%20I%20have%20access%20to%20the%20tools%20I%20need%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Moko.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConvincing%20his%20parents%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20hard.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20told%20them%20that%20I%20am%20going%20with%20music%20full-time%20and%20moving%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F240763%2Fnagaland-shiitake-oyster-mushrooms-earns-lakhs-how-to-grow-spores-method-scientist-innovation-agritech-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDimapur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20said%20that%20I%20was%20old%20enough%20to%20make%20my%20decisions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FMoko-Koza-Image-3-1700749674.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22