a.com%2F%3Fp%3D334652%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ujjwala%20Sahane%20was%20contemplating%20ending%20her%20life%20when%20her%20daughter%20had%20a%20fall%20that%20left%20her%20deaf%20and%20paralysed.%20A%20Bharatnatyam%20dancer%20today%2C%20this%20is%20her%20story%20of%20hope.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334652%2Fujjwala-sahane-prerana-hearing-impaired-deaf-bharatnatyam-dancer-soul-story%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Doctor%20Returned%20From%20The%20US%20To%20Build%20ISO-Certified%20Made-In-India%20Robot%20Making%20Surgeries%20Cheaper%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20brief%20encounter%20with%20a%20patient%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20Dr%20Sudhir%20Srivastava%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311579%2Fcardiologist-dr-deepak-krishnamurthy-breaks-myth-heart-attack-pain-relief-viral-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20renowned%20cardiologist%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20SS%20Innovations%2C%20experienced%20a%20transformative%20shift%20in%20perspective%20regarding%20his%20work.%20This%20encounter%20took%20place%20during%20a%20fateful%20visit%20to%20India%2C%20which%20ultimately%20served%20as%20a%20catalyst%20in%20his%20journey%20to%20develop%20made-in-India%20surgical%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20involved%20a%2022-year-old%20female%20diagnosed%20with%20an%20atrial%20septal%20defect%20%E2%80%94%20a%20congenital%20heart%20condition%20characterised%20by%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20septum%2C%20the%20wall%20that%20separates%20the%20heart%E2%80%99s%20upper%20chambers%20(atria).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20diagnosed%20quite%20late%20and%20was%20in%20a%20critical%20condition.%20The%20hospital%20was%20charging%20Rs%204%20lakh%20for%20the%20surgery%2C%20and%20her%20brother%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20it.%20While%20the%20doctor%20volunteered%20to%20do%20it%20for%20free%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263106%2Finspiring-ahmednagar-doctor-couple-free-rescue-homeless-destitute-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20hospital%20did%20not.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20brother%20asked%20for%20some%20time%20and%20tried%20to%20raise%20the%20money%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20I%20never%20heard%20from%20them%20again.%20To%20be%20honest%2C%20it%20still%20haunts%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Sudhir%20recalls%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20left%20him%20with%20sleepless%20nights%20and%20a%20mission%20%E2%80%94%20to%20develop%20a%20cost-effective%20system%20that%20can%20help%20people%20from%20every%20background%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outcome%20was%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20surgical%20robot%20called%20SSI%20Mantra.%20This%20innovative%20technology%20assists%20doctors%20in%20conducting%20complex%20surgeries%20with%20precision%20and%20ease%2C%20reducing%20costs%20by%20one-third%20compared%20to%20manual%20surgeries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20science%20company%20with%20a%20mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Dr%20Sudhir%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20in%201972%20for%20his%20postgraduate%20studies.%20He%20completed%20his%20residency%20in%20Cardiothoracic%20Surgery%20at%20the%20University%20of%20British%20Columbia%20in%20Vancouver%2C%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20practised%20for%20some%20years%20in%20Texas%20before%20becoming%20the%20founding%20chairman%20of%20Alliance%20Hospital%2C%20a%20centre%20for%20cardiovascular%20disease%20in%20West%20Texas%2C%20along%20with%2010%20other%20physicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20556px)%20100vw%2C%20556px%5C